84
00:03:59,390 --> 00:04:02,220
Rather than take blame for the cover up for
the virus,

85
00:04:02,220 --> 00:04:06,209
the Communist Party is trying to paint the
unquarantined people of Wuhan

86
00:04:06,209 --> 00:04:09,440
